comment: Bogdanovic (BKN) does not beat Middleton (MIL) to the spot as he tries to cut off the drive to the basket.
Middleton (MIL) legally takes 2 steps after the gather before he makes the pass on the drive to the basket.
Lopez (BKN) makes contact with the backboard, but it does not affect the layup attempt by Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Young (BKN) trips Antetokounmpo (MIL) on the drive to the basket causing him to fall to the floor.
Lopez (BKN) sets the screen on Carter-Williams (MIL) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Lopez (BKN) is in legal guarding position and does not affect Middleton's (MIL) drive toward the basket.
Carter-Williams (MIL) and Pachulia (MIL) contest the running floater by Jack (BKN) without affecting his play to the basket. His momentum initiates incidental contact with Pachulia.
Johnson (BKN) commits a take foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Johnson (BKN) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) lock arms but quickly separate.
Pachulia (MIL) sets the screen on Johnson (BKN) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction. The contact is incidental.
Pachulia (MIL) sets the screen on Anderson (BKN) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Young (BKN) and Ilyasova (MIL) clamp one another while battling for rebounding position.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes "high five" contact with Johnson (BKN) after his follow through.
Lopez (BKN) maintains legal guarding position as he contests the driving layup attempt by Pachulia (MIL).
Anderson (BKN) runs into Ilyasova (MIL) while trying to secure the loose ball, causing him to fall to the floor.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Lopez (BKN) was upheld and Milwaukee was awarded possession.
Jack (BKN) is not in a legal guarding position at the time of the contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Ilyasova (MIL) cleanly strips the ball from Lopez (BKN).
Bogdanovic (BKN) maintains legal guarding position on the drive into the lane by Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Middleton (MIL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Johnson (BKN).
Williams (BKN) pushes Middleton (MIL) and the contact affects his RSBQ on the perimeter.
Williams (BKN) pushes Carter-Williams (MIL) and the contact affects his movement to the basket.
Lopez (BKN) contests Carter-Williams' (MIL) layup attempt without affecting his movement to the basket.
Lopez (BKN) grabs Antetokounmpo (MIL) around the waist on the drive and affects his movement to the basket.
Lopez (BKN) makes incidental contact with Carter-Williams (MIL) going for the loose ball.
After Pachulia (MIL) rips the rebound away, Young (BKN) cleanly knocks the ball away.
Young (BKN) cleanly strips the ball from Pachulia (MIL).
Lopez (BKN) and Pachulia (MIL) both have their arms wrapped around one another while battling for rebounding position.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) knocks Jack's (BKN) hands away as he begins his drive to the basket.
Jack (BKN) makes contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) body and the contact affects his movement to the basket.
Ilyasova (MIL) makes contact with Young's (BKN) body and the contact affects his play at the basket.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) keeps a stayed forearm on Johnson (BKN) and affects his RSBQ at the start of the drive.
Lopez (BKN) extends his arm on the screen on Antetokounmpo (MIL) and does not give him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Ilyasova (MIL) makes contact with Lopez's (BKN) body on the made basket.
Carter-Williams (MIL) clamps Lopez' (BKN) arm, affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Lopez (BKN) clamps Pachulia's (MIL) arm going for the rebound and as he gains possession.
Young (BKN) keeps a stayed hand on Middleton (MIL) and the contact affects his RSBQ.
Lopez (BKN) maintains legal guarding position while contesting the layup attempt by Carter-Williams (MIL).
Carter-Williams (MIL) bumps Jack (BKN) on the baseline drive and affects his RSBQ.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) cleanly blocks the layup attempt by Young (BKN).
Bogdanovic (BKN) makes contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) to the body on the made basket.
Jack (BKN) is in legal guarding position on the drive by Carter-Williams (MIL).
Middleton (MIL) is inside the Restricted Area at the time of the contact with Young (BKN).
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes contact with Young (BKN) to the body as he attempts the layup.
Pachulia (MIL) legally contests the jump shot by Johnson (BKN).
Carter-Williams (MIL) commits a take foul on Jack (BKN).
Bayless (MIL) commits a take foul on Johnson (BKN).
